### **3. 24_LogPatternBoard**  
**Description:**  
Analyzes logs to detect message repetition, burst frequency, and keyword-based clustering.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LogPatternBoard - Frequency-Based Log Analyzer

LogPatternBoard simplifies log forensics by surfacing repeating patterns, warnings, and high-volume log clusters.

## Features
- Frequency counters  
- Timestamp-based burst detection  
- Keyword highlighting  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/24_LogPatternBoard.git
cd 24_LogPatternBoard
python analyze.py logs/system.log
